title: Week 16 Buy or Sell + Playoff Push, Permission to Cry - Fantasy Football Podcast for 12/22
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode heading into Week 16! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get ready for this week’s action with a handful of questions answered, injury updates, and a new edition of Buy or Sell! Plus, a preview of the Thursday Night matchup between the 49ers and Titans. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for December 22nd, 2021.
  
 (12:05) - Buy or Sell
 (18:20) - News & Notes
 (28:25) - Mailbag
 (30:20) - Baker Mayfield dynasty value?
 (33:30) - D.J. Moore or Odell Beckham Jr?
 (34:10) - Tom Brady or Taysom Hill? 
 (39:15) - Staying committed after elimination
 (41:05) - Dak Prescott
 (45:55) - Thursday Night Breakdown: 49ers at Titans
